              -arg-> obj-1 ]

OP 17 - "To find something with more something relative to something else ..."
  trig:
  FIND[ obj-1
         hq-1 -hq--> obj-1 
              -alt-> obj-2 ]
----------
   FCN[ fcn-1 -lex-  vis_enum 
              -arg-> obj-1 ] 

OP 18 - "To find something with a location relative to something visible ..."
  trig:
